metadata.name: Wet Pussay G
metadata.description:
The Amazing : Wet Pussay Gang // 3508 x 4961 // July, 2019

After tagging over the N.W.A ( Noobs With Attitude ) burners on East Graff City two main streets, The Warparty prepare to head home. However, Spray Head suggests that Little Caps should tag over the N.W.A burner on the side of their hangout. Ninja69 seems reluctant and Lil Caps makes his way to the hangout alone. Eventually Lil Caps is persuaded and his bike tire blow up. Can Wet Pussay survive the night ? Who knows !
